last_episode_to_air.name: The 1990s
last_episode_to_air.overview: In 1990s Britain, New Labour was emerging and the Spice Girls were soon to form. This episode explores how Diana became the emblem of a new spirit of emotional candour.

name: Diana's Decades
overview: Princess Diana was an icon who both captured and transformed the spirit of the times. Following how this thoroughly modern princess emerged from the bra-burning spirit of the 1970s and helped transform not just the Royal Family, but Britain itself.
